## Technical Notes

Hook response format: `{"decision":"allow|block","reason":"text"}` with exit code 0.

Tool names for this platform: `bash` → `run_shell_command`, `write` → `write_file`, 

=== install.js copies to: ===
  ~/.gemini/extensions/gm-gc/  (WITH -gc suffix)

=== THE PROBLEM ===
Gemini looks for ~/.gemini/extensions/gm/ (no -gc suffix)
But install.js copies to ~/.gemini/extensions/gm-gc/ (with -gc suffix)

